<plot>Lisa Rogers and Nicholas Cowell present a series in which four couples compete to create the best interior design in different apartments in the same block on a budget of 25 grand. The couples must also continue with their normal daily lives under the gaze of 24-hour TV surveillance - with underhand tactics to foil their competitors allowed. The completed properties will then be put up for auction - and the public will decide who wins.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?544666</url></doc>
